Description: The Jashn-e-Azaadi special episode starts with Kapil coming on the stage and wishing everyone for the 68th Independence Day. Kapil then speaks about the way he used to celebrate the Independence Day in school, and then a small AV is shown of the new show coming on colors - Udaan. Kapil then speaks about how the Independence Day is celebrated now-a-days. Dadi comes on the stage who tells Kapil that the King and Queen of Honolulu are coming as guests to their house. Kapil tells Dadi to care of them and leaves for a movie with his wife. Dadi and Ramu the welcome the guests to the show. Watch the special episode and enjoy the wonderful performances by a horde of actors Vishal Singh, Rashmi Desai, Dancing Wonder Akshat, Shakti Mohan, Karishma Tanna, Karan Wahi, Laccha, Pinky Bua, Kapil and many others.
